@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Route Handler\nGET /api/recommendations" as Route
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
participant "Recommendation Service" as Service
participant "Recommendation Repository" as Repository
database "Supabase DB\nonboarding, similarities" as Database

User -> Frontend: 맞춤 추천 조회
Frontend -> Route: GET /api/recommendations
Route -> Auth: 현재 세션 확인
Auth --> Route: userId 반환
Route -> Service: 맞춤 추천 요청
Service -> Repository: 온보딩 선호 영화 조회
Repository -> Database: user_onboarding_movies 조회
Database --> Repository: seed movies
Service -> Repository: 추천 후보 조회
Repository -> Database: movie_similarities, movie_stats 조회
Database --> Repository: recommendation rows
Repository --> Service: 추천 후보
Service --> Route: 추천 영화 목록
Route --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: 맞춤 추천 표시
@enduml
